{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889027166,"sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c06bb00188o4oMT0rFwAWw","messageID":"msg_d7b3bf3a9001u735P4Z4VzsyGD","sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_350fd8d8628a4e5e8da83904","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n4: Language: Go\n5: Size: L\n6: \n7: ## 测试任务清单\n8: \n9: ### 1. 核心配置测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go)\n10: - [ ] 测试 `DefaultConfig()` - 验证默认配置值正确\n11: - [ ] 测试 `LoadConfig()` - 环境变量的正确加载\n12:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 有效值\n13:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 无效值（错误处理）\n14:   - [ ] KUBECONFIG 环境变量\n15:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE 环境变量\n16:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD 有效/无效值\n17:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_DEBUG 环境变量\n18:   - [ ] 无环境变量时的默认行为\n19: \n20: ### 2. Server 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go)\n21: - [ ] 测试 `NewClient()` \n22:   - [ ] kubeconfig 文件路径提供时\n23:   - [ ] kubeconfig 为空时使用 InClusterConfig\n24:   - [ ] Kubernetes 配置创建失败时的错误处理\n25: - [ ] 测试 `NewServer()`\n26:   - [ ] 成功创建 server 实例\n27:   - [ ] gin 模式设置（debug/release）\n28:   - [ ] 依赖注入正确\n29: - [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n30:   - [ ] 正常启动流程\n31:   - [ ] context 取消时的关闭\n32:   - [ ] HTTP 服务错误处理\n33: - [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n34:   - [ ] 优雅关闭验证\n35: \n36: ### 3. Routes 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/routes_test.go)\n37: - [ ] 测试 `SetupRoutes()` - 路由正确注册\n38: - [ ] 验证所有端点正确绑定\n39: - [ ] 中间件正确应用\n40: \n41: ### 4. Handler 测试\n42: \n43: #### 4.1 AgentRuntime Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime_test.go)\n44: - [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeHandler()`\n45: - [ ] 测试 `CreateAgentRuntime()`\n46:   - [ ] 成功创建 AgentRuntime\n47:   - [ ] 无效 JSON 请求\n48:   - [ ] namespace 缺失\n49:   - [ ] name 缺失\n50:   - [ ] spec.container.image 缺失\n51:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误（NotFound, Conflict, Invalid）\n52: - [ ] 测试 `ListAgentRuntimes()`\n53:   - [ ] 成功返回列表\n54:   - [ ] namespace 参数验证\n55:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误处理\n56: - [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n57:   - [ ] 成功获取单个资源\n58:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n59:   - [ ] 参数验证\n60: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntime()`\n61:   - [ ] 成功更新\n62:   - [ ] name 不匹配错误\n63:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n64: - [ ] 测试 `DeleteAgentRuntime()`\n65:   - [ ] 成功删除\n66:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n67: \n68: #### 4.2 CodeInterpreter Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter_test.go)\n69: - [ ] 测试 `NewCodeInterpreterHandler()`\n70: - [ ] 测试 `CreateCodeInterpreter()`\n71:   - [ ] 成功创建\n72:   - [ ] 参数验证（namespace, name, image）\n73:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误\n74: - [ ] 测试 `ListCodeInterpreters()`\n75: - [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n76: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateCodeInterpreter()`\n77: - [ ] 测试 `DeleteCodeInterpreter()`\n78: \n79: #### 4.3 Sandbox Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go) **[待创建]**\n80: - [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxHandler()`\n81: - [ ] 测试 `HandleAgentRuntimeCreate()`\n82:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n83:   - [ ] 请求体验证\n84:   - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n85:   - [ ] sandbox 创建超时\n86: - [ ] 测试 `HandleCodeInterpreterCreate()`\n87:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n88:   - [ ] CodeInterpreter 不存在\n89:   - [ ] 创建失败回滚\n90: \n91: #### 4.4 Health Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/health_test.go)\n92: - [ ] 测试 `NewHealthHandler()`\n93: - [ ] 测试 `Health()` - 健康检查端点\n94: - [ ] 测试 `SetReady()` - 就绪状态设置\n95: \n96: ### 5. Processor 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor_test.go)\n97: \n98: #### 5.1 辅助函数测试\n99: - [ ] 测试 `RandString()` - 随机字符串生成\n100: - [ ] 测试 `GenerateSessionID()` - session ID 生成格式\n101: \n102: #### 5.2 Getter 函数测试\n103: - [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n104:   - [ ] 成功获取\n105:   - [ ] lister 为 nil\n106:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n107: - [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n108:   - [ ] 成功获取\n109:   - [ ] lister 为 nil\n110:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n111: \n112: #### 5.3 Build 函数测试\n113: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxObject()`\n114:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox 对象\n115:   - [ ] 随机后缀生成\n116:   - [ ] 标签和注解正确复制\n117:   - [ ] 容器配置正确转换（command, args, env）\n118:   - [ ] env 的不同类型处理（value, valueFrom）\n119: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxClaimObject()`\n120:   - [ ] 成功构建 claim 对象\n121:   - [ ] 标签正确设置\n122: - [ ] 测试 `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()`\n123:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox\n124:   - [ ] 容器配置正确\n125: \n126: #### 5.4 Pod IP 解析测试\n127: - [ ] 测试 `resolvePodIP()`\n128:   - [ ] pod 直接通过名称找到\n129:   - [ ] pod 未运行状态\n130:   - [ ] pod 无 IP\n131:   - [ ] 通过 label selector 查找\n132:   - [ ] 通过 owner reference 匹配\n133:   - [ ] pod 不存在\n134: \n135: #### 5.5 EntryPoint 构建测试\n136: - [ ] 测试 `BuildEntryPoints()` - 入口点正确构建\n137: \n138: #### 5.6 CreateSandbox 测试\n139: - [ ] 测试 `CreateSandbox()`\n140:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n141:   - [ ] 创建超时回滚\n142:   - [ ] pod 等待超时\n143:   - [ ] warm pool 模式\n144: \n145: #### 5.7 回滚测试\n146: - [ ] 测试 `rollback()` - sandbox 删除回滚\n147: \n148: ### 6. Reconciler 测试\n149: \n150: #### 6.1 Manager 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go) **[待创建]**\n151: - [ ] 测试 `DefaultReconcilerConfig()`\n152: - [ ] 测试 `NewControllerManager()`\n153:   - [ ] 成功创建\n154:   - [ ] 客户端配置（QPS, Burst）\n155:   - [ ] context 初始化\n156: - [ ] 测试 `AddReconciler()`\n157: - [ ] 测试 `SetupEventRecorder()`\n158: - [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n159: - [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n160: - [ ] 测试 getter 方法\n161: - [ ] 测试 `CalculateBackoff()` - 退避算法\n162: - [ ] 测试 `MapObjectReference()` - 对象引用映射\n163: \n164: #### 6.2 AgentRuntime Reconciler 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go) **[待创建]**\n165: - [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeReconciler()`\n166: - [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n167: - [ ] 测试 `processNextWorkItem()`\n168: - [ ] 测试 `Reconcile()`\n169:   - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n170:   - [ ] 删除时间戳设置（资源删除中）\n171:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建成功\n172:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（可重试错误）\n173:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（不可重试错误）\n174:   - [ ] 状态更新成功\n175:   - [ ] 状态更新失败\n176: - [ ] 测试 `getAgentRuntime()`\n177: - [ ] 测试 `reconcileDeletion()`\n178: - [ ] 测试 `reconcileSandboxPod()`\n179:   - [ ] pod 不存在时创建\n180:   - [ ] pod 存在时更新检查\n181: - [ ] 测试 `getSandboxPod()`\n182: - [ ] 测试 enqueue 方法\n183:   - [ ] `EnqueueAgentRuntime()`\n184:   - [ ] `EnqueueUpdate()`\n185:   - [ ] `EnqueueDelete()`\n186:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPod()`\n187:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodUpdate()`\n188:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodDelete()`\n189: \n190: #### 6.3 Status Updater 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go) **[待创建]**\n191: - [ ] 测试 `NewStatusUpdater()`\n192: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus()`\n193:   - [ ] 成功更新状态\n194:   - [ ] 更新失败重试\n195: \n196: #### 6.4 Sandbox Processor (Reconciler) 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go) **[待创建]**\n197: - [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxProcessor()`\n198: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n199: - [ ] 测试 `NeedsUpdate()` **[需查看实现]**\n200: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n201: \n202: #### 6.5 Owner Reference 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go) **[待创建]**\n203: - [ ] 测试 owner reference 相关函数\n204: \n205: #### 6.6 Error Handling 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go) **[待创建]**\n206: - [ ] 测试 `IsRetryableError()`\n207: - [ ] 测试错误常量定义\n208: \n209: ### 7. Garbage Collector 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go)\n210: - [ ] 测试 `NewGarbageCollector()`\n211: - [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n212: - [ ] 测试 `Stop()`\n213: - [ ] 测试 `gcLoop()`\n214: - [ ] 测试 `tick()`\n215:   - [ ] 空闲 sandbox 清理\n216:   - [ ] 过期 sandbox 清理\n217:   - [ ] store 错误处理\n218: - [ ] 测试 `deleteSandbox()`\n219:   - [ ] 成功删除 Sandbox\n220:   - [ ] 成功删除 SandboxClaim\n221:   - [ ] 删除失败（ NotFound 错误）\n222:   - [ ] 删除失败（其他错误）\n223:   - [ ] store 删除失败\n224: - [ ] 测试 `recordAudit()`\n225: \n226: ### 8. Middleware 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/request_id_test.go)\n227: - [ ] 测试 `RequestIDMiddleware()`\n228:   - [ ] 请求头已存在 X-Request-ID\n229:   - [ ] 请求头不存在时生成新 UUID\n230:   - [ ] 响应头正确设置\n231:   - [ ] context 中设置 request_id\n232: \n233: ### 9. Response 工具测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go)\n234: - [ ] 测试 `JSON()`\n235: - [ ] 测试 `Created()`\n236: - [ ] 测试 `Error()`\n237: - [ ] 测试 `ErrorWithID()`\n238: \n239: ### 10. Types 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go) **[待创建]**\n240: - [ ] 测试 `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate()`\n241:   - [ ] kind 为空\n242:   - [ ] kind 不是有效类型\n243:   - [ ] name 为空\n244:   - [ ] namespace 为空\n245:   - [ ] 验证通过\n246: - [ ] 验证常量定义\n247: \n248: ## 待创建测试文件列表\n249: 1. pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go\n250: 2. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go\n251: 3. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go\n252: 4. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go\n253: 5. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go\n254: 6. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go\n255: 7. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go\n256: 8. pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go\n257: \n258: ## 依赖与 Mock\n259: - 需要 Mock 的接口：\n260:   - dynamic.Interface\n261:   - kubernetes.Interface\n262:   - corev1lister.PodLister\n263:   - AgentRuntimeLister\n264:   - CodeInterpreterLister\n265:   - store.Store\n266:   - workqueue.RateLimitingInterface\n267:   - record.EventRecorder\n268: \n269: ## 测试覆盖率目标\n270: - 行覆盖率：≥80%\n271: - 分支覆盖率：≥70%\n272: - 关键路径 100% 覆盖\n\n(End of file - total 272 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\nModule: pkg/workloadmanager\nLanguage: Go\nSize: L\n\n## 测试任务清单\n\n### 1. 核心配置测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `DefaultConfig()` - 验证默认配置值正确\n- [ ] 测试 `LoadConfig()` - 环境变量的正确加载\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 有效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 无效值（错误处理）\n  - [ ] KUBECONFIG 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD 有效/无效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_DEBUG 环境变量\n  - [ ] 无环境变量时的默认行为\n\n### 2. Server 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775889027141,"end":1775889027164}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889027168,"sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c0b40001fhjlH6im0uC77w","messageID":"msg_d7b3bf3a9001u735P4Z4VzsyGD","sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_6e1ab455c578425fa1203cd2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: ## 1. Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块及其子包（特别是 `reconciler` 包）编写全面的 Go 单元测试，确保代码质量、可维护性和可靠性。\n6: \n7: 本提案针对 AR-038 需求，覆盖以下核心组件：\n8: - **Reconciler 框架**: `ControllerManager`, `AgentRuntimeReconciler`, `StatusUpdater`, `SandboxProcessor`\n9: - **工具函数**: Owner reference 管理、错误处理、指标收集\n10: - **Garbage Collector**: 沙箱清理逻辑\n11: - **Handler 层**: HTTP 请求处理（已有部分测试）\n12: - **Middleware**: 请求中间件（已有部分测试）\n13: \n14: ## 2. Scope\n15: \n16: ### 2.1 In Scope\n17: \n18: | 文件 | 优先级 | 测试类型 |\n19: |------|--------|----------|\n20: | `reconciler/manager.go` | P0 | 单元测试 |\n21: | `reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler.go` | P0 | 单元测试 + 集成测试 |\n22: | `reconciler/status_updater.go` | P0 | 单元测试 |\n23: | `reconciler/sandbox_processor.go` | P0 | 单元测试 |\n24: | `reconciler/interface.go` | P1 | 单元测试 |\n25: | `reconciler/owner_reference.go` | P1 | 单元测试 |\n26: | `reconciler/errors.go` | P1 | 单元测试 |\n27: | `reconciler/metrics.go` | P2 | 单元测试 |\n28: | `garbage_collector.go` | P1 | 单元测试 |\n29: | `reconciler/design.md` | - | 参考文档 |\n30: \n31: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n32: \n33: - E2E 测试（由单独的测试计划覆盖）\n34: - 性能/负载测试\n35: - 已覆盖的 handler 和 middleware 测试的重复编写\n36: \n37: ## 3. Impact Analysis\n38: \n39: ### 3.1 代码依赖\n40: \n41: ```\n42: pkg/workloadmanager/\n43: ├── reconciler/\n44: │   ├── manager.go              → 依赖 k8s client-go, dynamic client\n45: │   ├── agentruntime_reconciler.go → 依赖 manager, status_updater, sandbox_processor\n46: │   ├── status_updater.go       → 依赖 dynamic client, k8s API types\n47: │   ├── sandbox_processor.go    → 依赖 k8s client, API types\n48: │   ├── interface.go            → 依赖 workqueue, cache\n49: │   ├── owner_reference.go      → 纯工具函数，无外部依赖\n50: │   ├── errors.go               → 纯工具函数，无外部依赖\n51: │   └── metrics.go              → 无外部依赖\n52: ├── garbage_collector.go        → 依赖 dynamic client, store interface\n53: ├── handler/                    → 已有测试\n54: ├── middleware/                 → 已有测试\n55: └── types/                      → 数据类型定义\n56: ```\n57: \n58: ### 3.2 测试基础设施需求\n59: \n60: 1. **Fake Clients**: 使用 `client-go` 提供的 fake clientset 和 dynamic client\n61: 2. **Test Fixtures**: 创建通用的测试对象构建器（AgentRuntime, Pod, etc.）\n62: 3. **Mock Store**: 为 garbage collector 实现 mock store interface\n63: 4. **Table-driven Tests**: 广泛使用表驱动测试模式\n64: \n65: ### 3.3 预期工作量\n66: \n67: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估时间 |\n68: |------|------|----------|\n69: | Phase 1 | 搭建测试基础设施 + owner_reference.go, errors.go, metrics.go | 4h |\n70: | Phase 2 | sandbox_processor.go 单元测试 | 6h |\n71: | Phase 3 | status_updater.go 单元测试 | 6h |\n72: | Phase 4 | manager.go 单元测试 | 4h |\n73: | Phase 5 | agentruntime_reconciler.go 单元测试 | 8h |\n74: | Phase 6 | garbage_collector.go 单元测试 | 4h |\n75: | Phase 7 | 集成测试 + 测试覆盖率分析 | 4h |\n76: | **总计** | | **36h** |\n77: \n78: ## 4. Alternatives Considered\n79: \n80: ### 4.1 方案 A: 仅使用 Fake Clients（推荐）\n81: \n82: **描述**: 使用 `client-go` 官方提供的 fake clientset 和 dynamic client\n83: \n84: **优点**:\n85: - 与真实 client 行为一致\n86: - 无需维护额外的 mock 代码\n87: - 支持 informer/cache 相关测试\n88: \n89: **缺点**:\n90: - 部分场景需要手动管理 indexer\n91: - 无法模拟所有 API server 错误场景\n92: \n93: **采用原因**: 最接近真实场景，社区标准做法\n94: \n95: ### 4.2 方案 B: 使用 Mock 框架（gomock/mockery）\n96: \n97: **描述**: 为 interfaces 生成 mock 实现\n98: \n99: **优点**:\n100: - 灵活控制返回值和行为\n101: - 可验证调用顺序和次数\n102: \n103: **缺点**:\n104: - 需要维护 mock 代码\n105: - mock 行为可能与真实实现不一致\n106: - 增加项目依赖\n107: \n108: **不采用原因**: 增加维护成本，且 fake clients 已足够\n109: \n110: ### 4.3 方案 C: 使用 envtest（Kubernetes 测试框架）\n111: \n112: **描述**: 启动真实的 API server 进行测试\n113: \n114: **优点**:\n115: - 最接近真实环境\n116: - 可测试 admission webhook 等高级特性\n117: \n118: **缺点**:\n119: - 测试执行慢（需要启动 API server）\n120: - 依赖 etcd 和 API server 二进制文件\n121: - 不适合快速迭代的单元测试\n122: \n123: **不采用原因**: 适合作为集成测试补充，但不适合作为单元测试主力\n124: \n125: ## 5. Test Strategy\n126: \n127: ### 5.1 测试分层\n128: \n129: ```\n130: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n131: │        Integration Tests            │  ← 使用 envtest（可选）\n132: ├─────────────────────────────────────┤\n133: │      Unit Tests (Fake Clients)      │  ← 主要测试层\n134: ├─────────────────────────────────────┤\n135: │      Unit Tests (Pure Functions)    │  ← 基础测试\n136: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n137: ```\n138: \n139: ### 5.2 覆盖率目标\n140: \n141: - **Line Coverage**: ≥ 80%\n142: - **Branch Coverage**: ≥ 70%\n143: - **核心模块** (reconciler/*): ≥ 85%\n144: \n145: ### 5.3 测试命名规范\n146: \n147: ```go\n148: // 格式：Test[FunctionName][Scenario]_[ExpectedResult]\n149: func TestAgentRuntimeReconciler_Reconcile_NotFound_ReturnsEmpty(t *testing.T)\n150: func TestSandboxProcessor_BuildSandboxPod_Success(t *testing.T)\n151: func TestStatusUpdater_UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus_NilPod_SetsPending(t *testing.T)\n152: ```\n153: \n154: ### 5.4 表驱动测试模板\n155: \n156: ```go\n157: func TestXxx(t *testing.T) {\n158:     tests := []struct {\n159:         name        string\n160:         input       InputType\n161:         expected    ExpectedType\n162:         expectError bool\n163:     }{\n164:         {\"scenario1\", input1, expected1, false},\n165:         {\"scenario2\", input2, expected2, true},\n166:     }\n167:     \n168:     for _, tt := range tests {\n169:         t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n170:             // test logic\n171:         })\n172:     }\n173: }\n174: ```\n175: \n176: ## 6. Test Cases Detail\n177: \n178: ### 6.1 owner_reference.go (P1)\n179: \n180: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n181: |------|----------|\n182: | `SetControllerReference` | 正常添加、多次添加 |\n183: | `IsOwnedBy` | 是所有者、不是所有者、无 owner |\n184: | `GetControllerUID` | 有 controller、无 controller |\n185: | `HasOwnerReference` | 存在、不存在 |\n186: | `AddOwnerReference` | 添加 controller/non-controller |\n187: | `RemoveOwnerReference` | 移除存在/不存在的 UID |\n188: | `FindOwnedObjects` | 过滤 owned 对象 |\n189: | `HasFinalizer` | 存在/不存在 |\n190: | `AddFinalizer` | 添加已存在/不存在的 finalizer |\n191: | `RemoveFinalizer` | 移除 finalizer |\n192: | `IsBeingDeleted` | 有/无 deletion timestamp |\n193: | `IsReadyToCleanup` | 满足/不满足清理条件 |\n194: \n195: ### 6.2 errors.go (P1)\n196: \n197: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n198: |------|----------|\n199: | `ReconcileError.Error()` | 错误消息格式 |\n200: | `ReconcileError.Unwrap()` | 错误包装 |\n201: | `IsRetryableError()` | 可重试/不可重试错误类型 |\n202: | `NewReconcileError()` | 创建错误实例 |\n203: \n204: ### 6.3 metrics.go (P2)\n205: \n206: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n207: |------|----------|\n208: | `ObserveReconcileDuration()` | 记录耗时 |\n209: | `RecordError()` | 错误计数 |\n210: | `RecordReconcile()` | 协调计数 |\n211: | `GetAverageReconcileTime()` | 零次/多次协调 |\n212: | `NoOpMetrics` | 空操作验证 |\n213: \n214: ### 6.4 sandbox_processor.go (P0)\n215: \n216: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n217: |------|----------|\n218: | `BuildSandboxPod()` | 正常构建、带 labels/annotations、带 code interpreter |\n219: | `BuildCodeInterpreterPod()` | 正常构建 |\n220: | `buildPodSpec()` | 资源配额、网络策略、 volumes |\n221: | `buildResourceRequirements()` | nil quota、完整 quota、部分 quota |\n222: | `buildContainerPorts()` | 默认端口、自定义端口 |\n223: | `NeedsUpdate()` | 需要更新/不需要更新 |\n224: | `UpdateSandboxPod()` | 删除并重建 |\n225: \n226: ### 6.5 status_updater.go (P0)\n227: \n228: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n229: |------|----------|\n230: | `UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus()` | nil pod、running pod、failed pod |\n231: | `UpdateCodeInterpreterStatus()` | 类似 AgentRuntime |\n232: | `mapPodPhaseToRuntimePhase()` | 各 pod phase 映射 |\n233: | `buildConditionsFromPod()` | pod conditions 转换 |\n234: | `updateAgentRuntimeStatusSubresource()` | status 更新（fake client） |\n235: \n236: ### 6.6 manager.go (P0)\n237: \n238: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n239: |------|----------|\n240: | `NewControllerManager()` | 正常创建、配置验证 |\n241: | `AddReconciler()` | 添加 reconciler |\n242: | `SetupEventRecorder()` | event recorder 配置 |\n243: | `Start()` / `Shutdown()` | 生命周期管理 |\n244: | `CalculateBackoff()` | 各 retry count 的延迟 |\n245: | `MapObjectReference()` | 对象引用转换 |\n246: \n247: ### 6.7 agentruntime_reconciler.go (P0)\n248: \n249: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n250: |------|----------|\n251: | `NewAgentRuntimeReconciler()` | 初始化验证 |\n252: | `Reconcile()` | Not Found、Deletion、正常协调、错误处理 |\n253: | `processNextWorkItem()` | workqueue 处理逻辑 |\n254: | `getAgentRuntime()` | 存在/不存在 |\n255: | `reconcileDeletion()` | 删除场景 |\n256: | `reconcileSandboxPod()` | Pod 不存在、存在需更新、存在无需更新 |\n257: | `getSandboxPod()` | 通过 name 查找、通过 selector 查找 |\n258: | `Enqueue*()` | 各类 enqueue 场景 |\n259: \n260: ### 6.8 garbage_collector.go (P1)\n261: \n262: | 函数 | 测试场景 |\n263: |------|----------|\n264: | `NewGarbageCollector()` | 初始化 |\n265: | `Start()` / `Stop()` | 生命周期 |\n266: | `gcLoop()` | 定时执行（mock ticker） |\n267: | `tick()` | idle timeout、expired timeout |\n268: | `deleteSandbox()` | 成功删除、API 错误、store 错误 |\n269: \n270: ## 7. Implementation Plan\n271: \n272: ### Phase 1: 基础设施 + 基础工具 (4h)\n273: ```\n274: - [ ] 创建测试工具包：pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/testing/helpers.go\n275: - [ ] 创建测试 fixtures：pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/testing/fixtures.go\n276: - [ ] owner_reference_test.go\n277: - [ ] errors_test.go\n278: - [ ] metrics_test.go\n279: ```\n280: \n281: ### Phase 2: Sandbox Processor (6h)\n282: ```\n283: - [ ] sandbox_processor_test.go (完整覆盖)\n284: - [ ] 包含表驱动测试\n285: ```\n286: \n287: ### Phase 3: Status Updater (6h)\n288: ```\n289: - [ ] status_updater_test.go\n290: - [ ] 使用 fake dynamic client\n291: ```\n292: \n293: ### Phase 4: Manager (4h)\n294: ```\n295: - [ ] manager_test.go\n296: - [ ] 测试 event recorder\n297: ```\n298: \n299: ### Phase 5: AgentRuntime Reconciler (8h)\n300: ```\n301: - [ ] agentruntime_reconciler_test.go\n302: - [ ] 集成 informer/cache 测试\n303: ```\n304: \n305: ### Phase 6: Garbage Collector (4h)\n306: ```\n307: - [ ] garbage_collector_test.go\n308: - [ ] Mock store interface\n309: ```\n310: \n311: ### Phase 7: 集成与验证 (4h)\n312: ```\n313: - [ ] 运行测试覆盖率：go test -coverprofile=cover.out\n314: - [ ] 生成覆盖率报告：go tool cover -html=cover.out\n315: - [ ] 确保覆盖率达标\n316: - [ ] 修复 failing tests\n317: ```\n318: \n319: ## 8. Success Criteria\n320: \n321: 1. ✅ 所有新增测试通过\n322: 2. ✅ 整体覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n323: 3. ✅ 核心模块覆盖率 ≥ 85%\n324: 4. ✅ 无数据竞争（`go test -race` 通过）\n325: 5. ✅ 测试可重复运行（无状态污染）\n326: 6. ✅ CI/CD 集成通过\n327: \n328: ## 9. Dependencies\n329: \n330: - Go 1.21+\n331: - Kubernetes client-go v0.34.1\n332: - 项目现有 test infrastructure\n333: \n334: ## 10. References\n335: \n336: - [Kubernetes Testing Guide](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-testing/testing.md)\n337: - [client-go testing](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go/tree/master/testing)\n338: - `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/design.md` - 详细设计文档\n339: - `deployment/client-go.md` - client-go 生成代码说明\n\n(End of file - total 339 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n## 1. Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块及其子包（特别是 `reconciler` 包）编写全面的 Go 单元测试，确保代码质量、可维护性和可靠性。\n\n本提案针对 AR-038 需求，覆盖以下核心组件：\n- **Reconciler 框架**: `ControllerManager`, `AgentRuntimeReconciler`, `StatusUpdater`, `SandboxProcessor`\n- **工具函数**: Owner reference 管理、错误处理、指标收集\n- **Garbage Collector**: 沙箱清理逻辑\n- **Handler 层**: HTTP 请求处理（已有部分测试）\n- **Middleware**: 请求中间件（已有部分测试）\n\n## 2. Scope\n\n### 2.1 In Scope\n\n| 文件 | 优先级 | 测试类型 |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| `reconciler/manager.go` | P0 | 单元测试 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775889027144,"end":1775889027166}}}}
