{"type":"text","timestamp":1775889057838,"sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c607b001SgDC3swvIS4Iko","messageID":"msg_d7b3c53aa0012Fw7aDJxW0X12M","sessionID":"ses_284c4312fffedYJ0dltqH0s15N","type":"text","text":"## Archive: AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** L  \n**Status:** Scaffold/Partial Implementation\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n1. **测试基础设施**\n   - Scaffold 创建完成\n   - Proposal 文档完成 (339 行详细设计)\n\n2. **已实现的测试文件** (10 个文件)\n   - `config_test.go` - 配置加载测试\n   - `server_test.go` - Server 生命周期测试\n   - `routes_test.go` - 路由注册测试\n   - `handler/agent_runtime_test.go` - AgentRuntime CRUD 测试\n   - `handler/code_interpreter_test.go` - CodeInterpreter CRUD 测试\n   - `handler/health_test.go` - 健康检查测试\n   - `processor/sandbox_processor_test.go` - Sandbox 构建测试\n   - `garbage_collector_test.go` - GC 清理逻辑测试\n   - `middleware/request_id_test.go` - RequestID 中间件测试\n   - `response/response_test.go` - 响应工具测试\n\n3. **Reconciler 核心测试** (6 个文件)\n   - `reconciler/errors_test.go` - 错误处理测试\n   - `reconciler/metrics_test.go` - 指标收集测试\n   - `reconciler/owner_reference_test.go` - Owner Reference 工具测试\n   - `reconciler/manager_test.go` - Controller Manager 测试\n   - `reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go` - Sandbox Processor 测试\n   - `reconciler/status_updater_test.go` - 状态更新器测试\n\n---\n\n### ⏸ Deferred\n\n1. **待创建的测试文件** (8 个)\n   - `handler/sandbox_test.go` - Sandbox Handler 集成测试\n   - `reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go` - AgentRuntime Reconciler 协调逻辑测试（核心 P0）\n   - `types/sandbox_types_test.go` - 类型验证测试\n\n2. **未完成的覆盖率验证**\n   - 覆盖率报告未生成\n   - `go test -race` 数据竞争检测未执行\n\n3. **集成测试**\n   - Reconciler 全链路集成测试\n   - envtest 环境测试（可选）\n\n---\n\n**Next Steps:** 完成 `agentruntime_reconciler_test.go` (P0) 和覆盖率验证后可进入 review 阶段。","time":{"start":1775889057834,"end":1775889057834}}}
